Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Hip MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Articular effusion' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

And 'Small' radio button is enabled
And 'Moderate' radio button is enabled
And 'Pronounced' radio button is enabled

And 'Hemorrhagic' checkbox is enabled
And 'Empyema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Hemorrhagic' checkbox
Then 'Sedimentation' checkbox is enabled

When I select any diagnosis from 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled
